Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan budget defeated
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkc3
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Mar 1985
President Reagan's cost-cutting budget soundly defeated by the Senate committee which instead demands defence spending is trimmed. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less